<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Job Details Card</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="job-details.css"> <!-- Your custom CSS -->
</head>
<body>

  <div class="job-card shadow-sm">
    <div class="job-header">
      <h3 class="mb-0">Frontend Developer</h3>
      <small>Posted by: ABC Pvt Ltd · Bangalore, India</small>
    </div>
    <div class="job-body">
      <p><strong>Job Type:</strong> Full-Time</p>
      <p><strong>Salary:</strong> ₹6,00,000 – ₹9,00,000 per annum</p>
      <p><strong>Experience:</strong> 0–2 Years</p>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> We're looking for a passionate frontend developer to join our team and work on high-impact web applications. You'll collaborate with designers and backend developers to deliver seamless UI experiences.</p>
      
      <p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Build responsive and user-friendly interfaces using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</li>
        <li>Integrate with REST APIs and backend systems</li>
        <li>Write clean, maintainable, and reusable code</li>
        <li>Collaborate with the UX and product teams</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Required Skills:</strong></p>
      <div>
        <span class="badge-skill">HTML</span>
        <span class="badge-skill">CSS</span>
        <span class="badge-skill">JavaScript</span>
        <span class="badge-skill">React</span>
        <span class="badge-skill">Git</span>
      </div>

      <div class="text-end mt-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Apply Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
